==Japanese==
===Etymology===
{{ja-kanjitab-top}}
! [[水]] || [[無]] || [[月]]
{{ja-kanjitab-bottom}}
[[水]] (みず, ''mizu''), "water" + [[無]] (な, ''na'') as a [[euphonious]] but meaningless [[当て字]] (''[[w:Ateji|ateji]]'') + [[月]] (つき, ''tsuki''), "month"

===Noun===
'''水無月''' ([[みなつき]], ''minatsuki'')

# {{archaic}} the sixth month of the lunar calendar
# {{poetic}} the month of water; [[June]]

====Alternate pronunciation====
みなずき (''minazuki'')

